  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nIt would be really nice to easily spin up local testnets for 4844. We have [these scripts](https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/tree/stable/scripts/local_testnet) which we could extend to work through 4844. Or we could work to make some sort of set up that spawns lighthouse processes in rust, which would make it a lot easier to monitor behavior in the network (because we have clients for all APIs available). We could write more fine grained testing like this too. I had previously done some work towards this here: https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/pull/2960/files#diff-8f562ef9afba682c4ca170cc21dd6275f0905a0c2640243a3f31e8d178884cdd",
